rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Perhaps because there are many merchants
among us Nopon, we tend to prioritize
efficiency in everything, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0002
rows.name: This is also reflected in our food, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Use a lot of oil and stir-fry
quickly over high heat...
and it's done, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Nopon cuisine is the most efficient
meal, ready in an instant and
packed with nutrition, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0005
rows.name:
By the way, I'm good at making
Plump Fried Rice while browsing
through historical documents, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Of course, the precious documents
get covered in oil... mo.
